--------------------Summary----------------
eVuln ID: EV0085
CVE: CVE-2006-0877
Software: Easy Forum
Sowtware's Web Site: http://hot-things.net/?q=eforum
Versions: 2.5
Critical Level: Harmless
Type: Cross-Site Scripting
Class: Remote
Status: Patched
Exploit: Available
